description.narrative: Train, Eval & Oth Related Act. TRAIN, EVAL & OTH RELATED ACT[Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.]. Information has been redacted in accordance with the two principled exceptions defined in the Foreign Aid Transparency and Accountability Act (FATAA) of 2016: the health and security of implementing partners, and the national interest of the United States.. Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.
